The '''Domain Lah worldship''' was the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Koros-Strohna|worldship]] possessed by [[Domain Lah]].

==History==
After the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Fall]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and the death of the ''[[Baanu Rass]]'' during the [[Mission to Myrkr]], the [[Domain Lah]] [[Koros-Strohna|worldship]] was stationed in orbit around [[Myrkr/Legends|Myrkr]], and was used as a teaching place for members of the [[Warrior caste]].

